## 🔟 Przykłady rekrutacyjne

### 🔹 Ile dni do końca roku?

```java
LocalDate now = LocalDate.now();
LocalDate end = LocalDate.of(now.getYear(), 12, 31);

long days = ChronoUnit.DAYS.between(now, end);
```

---

### 🔹 Sprawdź czy termin minął

```java
boolean expired = ChronoUnit.DAYS.between(deadline, LocalDate.now()) > 0;
```

